            "container_size": "small",
            "text_horizontal": "left"
          }
        },
        "db1f9228-8e89-4592-855b-7bf8a842e21d": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Beyond just selling paintings, we are committed to fostering a vibrant community of artists and art lovers. Our store is a hub for artistic dialogue, offering workshops, exhibitions, and events that connect people with the beauty of art. We believe that art should be inclusive and accessible, which is why we provide personalized guidance and services to help you find the perfect piece that resonates with your soul and decor. </p>",
            "text_color": "heading",
            "text_size": "small",
            "container_size": "small",
            "text_horizontal": "left"
          }
        }
